In order to run this script, Python 3 with pathlib and toml must be present.
Example:
    module load anaconda3
    # create and activate a conda environment, if you do not want to install globally
    conda install pathlib toml scipy pandas pyarrow

    edit config.toml:
        - each step can be skipped by setting skip = true
        - all given paths must be absolute or relative to the location of the config.toml       

